text:
Think the shop may have changed owner. The drinks are not bad today. Milo C is $1.70, very thick and chocolatey. Nice!
The coffee shop seems to have been renovated too. Very spacious, bright and clean.

In 2023….
The coffee sucks!  No standard. The coffee especially, it is so tasteless. Smelt mainly of other mixes instead of coffee.  The service was good but we go for the breakfast, not the service. So don’t come here for breakfast.

New Indian Muslim store Al Amaan and best Muslim store thus far
-Generous chicken brayani for $6
-Decent Prata, Tosai and Maggie Goreng
Drinks are expensive here. The Mala stall pretty good. For a price of a western steak, sometimes you gotta go for SiChuan delights. Medium spicy was just nice for the kicks.
Big mouth mala is tasty and value for money. Korean Japanese food and kopi are decent.
The coffeeshop is not clean…full of cockroaches running around…they really need to do something about the cleanliness of the coffeeshop!
